Set's git username for individuals and pairs from their github profiles

  $ iam quackingduck
  $ git config --global user.name
  Myles Byrne
  $ git config --global user.email
  myles@myles.id.au

  $ weare quackingduck mweitzel
  Matthew Weitzel & Myles Byrne
  $ git config --global user.email
  pair+mweitzel.quackingduck@devbootcamp.com

For pairs:

 - The person with alphanumerically lower github username is always sorted first
 - The special email address pair+{user1}.{user2}@devbootcamp.com is used, this
   routes mail to pair@devbootcamp.com which will bounce any mail sent to it.
